text: The Domino Kid is a 1957 American western movie directed by Ray Nazarro and starring Rory Calhoun, Kristine Miller, Andrew Duggan, Yvette Dugay, Peter Whitney, Eugene Iglesias. It was distributed by Columbia Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1957 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by Ray Nazarro
